title: Tibia 8.11: Blackd Light Hack
description:
Blackd Light is a bit more than a simple light for Tibia.
This program let you configure the delay between updates and the light level.



But the most cool feature is changing the color of the light.
Try walking with green light - infravision !
Try walking with red light - vampire mode !
Try walking with gray light - old times images !


And the light will be applied to every one of your multiclients! (if available)



This tool was not created by me, all credits go to Blackd Tools.
